<L>__{exterior brinnlitz camp same time night}
<A>__{on a watchtower, a night sentry, unsure where it's coming from, listens to the distant singing. it seems like it's emanating from the surrounding hills, from the trees.}
<L>__{interior liepold's quarters same time night}
<A>__{at his small desk, liepold is typing a letter, denouncing schindler most likely. the pounding keys bury all other sounds but when he pauses to reread what he's typed, he hears it, the singing, faint, far away. he goes to his window, peers out, listens for a moment more, then hears nothing. only the night creatures.}
